A simple mod that changes some behaviours around vehicles.

Features:
- Adjustable Percentage of Vanilla spawn rate for Motorbike, Scooters, SUVs, Pickups, Vans and more
- Adjusted Max Speeds, Acceleration and Braking Power for all Vanilla Vehicles
- Reduced Acceleration and Braking Power for Trains for more realistic behaviour

Planned Features:
- Detailed Settings for vehicle type behaviour
- Add option to service buildings to select vehicles that can be spawned by that building
